{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be artistic and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artistic SaaS</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f8f8;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scroll */\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d32f2f 0%, #e57373 100%);\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .abstract-shapes {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .abstract-shapes::before,\n        .abstract-shapes::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            filter: blur(120px);\n        }\n\n        .abstract-shapes::before {\n            width: 300px;\n            height: 300px;\n            top: -50px;\n            left: -50px;\n        }\n\n        .abstract-shapes::after {\n            width: 250px;\n            height: 250px;\n            bottom: -70px;\n            right: -30px;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .feature-section {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .feature-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .feature-section h2::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -10px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background-color: #e57373;\n        }\n\n        .features-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: #fefefe;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #b71c1c;\n        }\n\n        .cta-section {\n            background-color: #d32f2f;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 -5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .cta-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-section p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            color: #d32f2f;\n            padding: 15px 35px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e57373;\n            color: #fff;\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            color: #aaa;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: #e57373;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        /* Artistic Elements */\n        .artistic-bg {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: -1;\n        }\n\n        .artistic-bg::before, .artistic-bg::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3) 0%, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0) 70%);\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            filter: blur(150px);\n        }\n\n        .artistic-bg::before {\n            width: 500px;\n            height: 500px;\n            top: -100px;\n            left: -150px;\n        }\n\n        .artistic-bg::after {\n            width: 400px;\n            height: 400px;\n            bottom: -100px;\n            right: -100px;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.4; }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.6; }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.4; }\n        }\n\n        .feature-item .icon-wrapper {\n            animation: pulse 3s infinite ease-in-out;\n            display: inline-block; /* Ensure it scales correctly */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item .icon-wrapper i {\n            margin-bottom: 0; /* Remove margin as animation wrapper handles spacing */\n        }\n\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"abstract-shapes\"></div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>VividFlow</h1>\n            <p>Unleash Your Creativity. Streamline Your Workflow.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"feature-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Empowering Your Vision</h2>\n            <div class=\"features-grid\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-palette\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>Intuitive Design</h3>\n                    <p>A beautifully crafted interface that inspires your best work. No steep learning curves, just pure creation.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>Dynamic Analytics</h3>\n                    <p>Gain deep insights into your project's progress with visually stunning and easy-to-understand data.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>Seamless Collaboration</h3>\n                    <p>Work together in real-time with your team, sharing ideas and feedback effortlessly.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-section\">\n        <div class=\"artistic-bg\"></div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Transform Your Process?</h2>\n            <p>Join the VividFlow community and experience the future of creative SaaS.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Free</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 VividFlow. All rights reserved. | <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add some subtle JavaScript effects if needed\n        document.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {\n            const header = document.querySelector('header');\n            const x = e.clientX / window.innerWidth - 0.5;\n            const y = e.clientY / window.innerHeight - 0.5;\n            header.style.backgroundPosition = `${-x * 20}px ${-y * 20}px`;\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}